<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/1753302-shiva"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1618794322i/1753302._UX100_CR0,31,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/1753302-shiva">Shiva</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">If your local library has a digital database, you might be able to get it there. I borrowed mine though my library and it had all the images and maps <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">If your local library has a digital database, you might be able to get it there. I borrowed mine though my library and it had all the images and maps as well. Hope this helps.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
